{"id":39162,"title":"[The choice of the endoscopic treatment method in patients with acute cholecystitis, complicated by choledocholithiasis].","abstract":"Peculiarities of the endoscopic methods application while treating 530 patients, suffering an acute cholecystitis, complicated by choledocholithiasis, were studied. Certain advantages of a two-staged treatment of the patients with initial management of biliary problems, using endoscopic retrograde cholangiography, were established.","date":"2014-09-25","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25252402","annotations":[{"name":"Endoscopy","weight":0.780462,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endoscopy"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.240731,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Cholecystitis","weight":0.208635,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cholecystitis"},{"name":"Choledocholithiasis","weight":0.0961346,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Choledocholithiasis"},{"name":"Bile duct","weight":0.0546925,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bile_duct"},{"name":"Suffering","weight":0.0280659,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suffering"},{"name":"Application software","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Application_software"},{"name":"Acute (medicine)","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_(medicine)"},{"name":"Retrograde motion","weight":0.0152478,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retrograde_motion"},{"name":"Cholangiography","weight":0.0148013,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cholangiography"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Area code 530","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Area_code_530"}]}
